text: National Highway 727G, commonly referred to as NH 727G is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 27. NH-727G runs in the state of Uttar Pradesh in India. == Route == NH727G connects Harraiya, Babhnan, Swaminarayan, Manakpur and Gonda in the state of Uttar Pradesh. == Junctions == : Terminal near Haraiya. : Terminal near Gonda. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 727G on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Uttar Pradesh
